      InstallShield  X  is  the most comprehensive all-in-one installation-
      authoring  solution for every platform, operating system, and device.
      InstallShield X enables developers to easily create Windows Installer
      (MSI), InstallScript, or cross-platform installations and extend them
      to  database  servers,  Web  services, and mobile devices C all while
      using  the  same,  easy-to-use interface. You select the installation
      technology  that  is  right  for  the situation. InstallShield X is a
      direct  upgrade  for  both  InstallShield DevStudio and InstallShield
      Multiplatform,  offering distinct and familiar project types for each
      group  of users. InstallShield X also features support for the latest
      technologies.  InstallShield  X  can  be run inside the Visual Studio
      .NET  IDE  and  fully supports .NET applications. Installations for a
      wide  range  of  Mobile Device applications can be created, including
      those  that  target  the  .NET  Compact  Framework. Web services, SQL
      Server, and 64-bit applications are supported, as well.

      For more information:
      http://www.installshield.com
